### Rupert AI Assistant API Requests
### Run the server first: poetry run python -m rupert.main

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8000/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Root endpoint (redirects to docs)
GET http://localhost:8000/
Accept: application/json

###

### Chat with Rupert - Basic greeting
POST http://localhost:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello Rupert"
}

###

### Chat with Rupert - Ask about yourself
POST http://localhost:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Tell me about yourself"
}

###

### Chat with Rupert - Ask about purpose
POST http://localhost:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What's your purpose?"
}

###

### Chat with Rupert - General question
POST http://localhost:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "What can you help me with?"
}

###

### Chat with Rupert - Invalid request (missing message)
POST http://localhost:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Chat with Rupert - Empty message
POST http://localhost:8000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": ""
}

###